This document describes the architecture
of the amiya.akn platform in a visual way
with all the components and how they
interact with each other.

g.title: Tailnet - Mesh VPN Network
UniFi Dream Machine Pro - Gateway & Network Controller
Home Network Attached Storage (NAS)
MinIO is a high-performance, distributed object storage system.
A self-hosted dashboard that puts all your feeds in one place.
Tailscale Connector for Kubernetes - Connects local network to tailnet
ArgoCD is a declarative, GitOps continuous delivery tool for Kubernetes.
Crossplane is an open-source Kubernetes add-on that extends your cluster with managed resources from any cloud or on-prem environment.
Talos Omni is a platform for managing Talos Linux clusters through a simplified interface.
Authelia is an open-source authentication and authorization server.
OpenBao secret management stack with PostgreSQL backend
yaLDAP is a modern LDAP server.
MinIO is a high-performance, distributed object storage system.
Zot Registry is a self-hosted, privacy-focused, and easy-to-use image registry.
Cert-Manager is a Kubernetes controller that automates the management and issuance of TLS certificates.
Cilium is a networking, observability, and security solution with an eBPF-based dataplane.
Envoy Gateway is a modern, open-source Kubernetes-native API gateway built on Envoy Proxy.
Envoy to proxy all HTTP/HTTPS traffic in the cluster.
Envoy to proxy all LDAP/LDAPS traffic in the cluster.
ExternalDNS is a Kubernetes controller that configures DNS resources.
External-Secret is a Kubernetes controller that allows you to use external secret management systems.
Longhorn is a distributed block storage system for Kubernetes.
TailScale is a mesh VPN that makes it easy to connect your devices, wherever they are.
CloudNative-PG is a Kubernetes operator for PostgreSQL management with advanced features like automated backups and high availability.
OpenBao is an open-source, community-driven fork of Vault managed by the Linux Foundation. Uses multi-mount topology with dedicated project mounts and shared/ mount.
PostgreSQL database backend for OpenBao, managed by CloudNative-PG operator with automated backups to S3.
